{"id":225,"date":"2007-08-27T19:00:39","date_gmt":"2007-08-27T19:00:39","guid":{"rendered":"http://192.168.5.119/2.2/?p=225"},"modified":"2007-08-27T19:00:39","modified_gmt":"2007-08-27T19:00:39","slug":"%e5%91%8a%e5%88%abthunderbird%ef%bc%8c%e5%9b%9e%e5%bd%92lotus-notes","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/%e5%91%8a%e5%88%abthunderbird%ef%bc%8c%e5%9b%9e%e5%bd%92lotus-notes.htm","title":{"rendered":"告别Thunderbird，回归Lotus Notes"},"content":{"rendered":"<div><font COLOR=\"#A6A6A6\">作者:xbeta　版本:070827/070827　出自:</font><a TITLE=\"善用佳软:精品免费软件。宣传最经典的免费软件及应用技巧。欢迎署名转载\" HREF=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/xbeta\" TARGET=\"_blank\"><font COLOR=\"#CC3333\">善用</font><font COLOR=\"#339999\">佳软</font><font COLOR=\"#A6A6A6\">blog.sina.com.cn/xbeta</font></a></div>\n<div>　　<img SRC=\"http://img120.imageshack.us/img120/8553/notesfb4.png\"></div>\n<div>\n　　将从070901起，邮件客户端（只用来收公司信件）从Thunderbird转回Lotus<br />\nNotes。</div>\n<div><strong>外界变化</strong>：</div>\n<div>　　2007-08-27，公司的Lotus<br />\nNotes从5.4升到了7.0（占了400MB空间）。除了速度快了一点、收信人输入中文不再乱码外，尚未感知到其他改进，也没有期望改进——因为Notes作为邮件客户端，管理功能是比较弱的；而作为OA的功能，用得极少。</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n<strong>转变原因</strong>：Notes的邮件管理功能在很多方面弱于Thunderbird，<strong>但</strong>：</div>\n<div>　　1.<br />\n但Notes是一定要用的。即便邮件用Thunderbird处理，通知、工作流也要打开Notes处理。</div>\n<p DIR=\"ltr\">　　2. 自己用Thunderbird对他人不便。</p>\n<p DIR=\"ltr\">　　2.1<br />\n工作邮件re来re去十几个回合（因而包含十几次引用）很正常，在Notes中形式很整齐，而用Thunderbird发出则差很多，令其他Notes用户不习惯。</p>\n<p DIR=\"ltr\">　　2.2<br />\nNotes的附件图标可出现在正文的指定位置，便于阅读。而Thunderbird发出的附件在Notes中会附到最后面，当有N次引用时，就会令收信人极度不便。</p>\n<p DIR=\"ltr\">　　3.<br />\n用Thunderbird自己也有不便，如无Notes在线地址本功能、发现新信速度不如Notes快。</p>\n<p DIR=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相应准备</strong>：</p>\n<p>　　1. 从07年9月1日开始用Notes，并承受邮件管理的不便。</p>\n<p>　　2. Notes邮件随时清理：删除垃圾邮件，外存附件。</p>\n<p>　　3.<br />\n定期清理邮件：服务器保留3个月邮件，更久的手工转至本地。</p>\n<p>　　4.<br />\n启用Notes日历功能，作为工作日志，定期通过打印方式存为pdf。</p>\n<p>　　5. 非工作邮件全用Gmail web方式处理。</p>\n<p>></iframe></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>作者:xbeta　版本:070827/070827　出自:善用佳软blog.sina.com.cn/xbeta [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":15,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["旧.网络相关","未分类"],"tags":["all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/225"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/15"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=225"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/225/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=225"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=225"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=225"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}